      <p class="bw-returns__copy">This page keeps the important parts easy to read: what qualifies for a return, when to raise a request, how cancellations work, and which larger items are supported through replacement instead of a full return.</p>
      <div class="bw-returns__chips">
        <span class="bw-returns__chip">Return window</span>
